title: RX Trivia - Radiology Quiz
description:
RX Trivia - Radiology Quiz was made with the aim of providing you with an intuitive, practical and fun tool with which you can study Radiology.

Choose the thematic axis you want to play, among the options you will have: X-rays, Magnetic Resonance and Computed Tomography.
Answer questions and advance through the different levels of difficulty.

You will be able to complete various challenges to get the "Collectibles", you will find everything from accessories, antennas, contrast media to equipment.
In each collectible you get you will see a brief description that will help you learn everything related to the world of Radiology.

We believe that one of the best ways to assimilate new study material or reaffirm concepts already seen is through a playful experience, which is why we invite you to download "RX Trivia - Radiology Quiz" for FREE, enjoy it!
